<p class="ap-story-p"><a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/news/donald-trump">Donald Trump Jr</a> is under increasing scrutiny after it was reported he was aware <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2017/07/10/us/politics/donald-trump-jr-russia-email-candidacy.html" target="_blank">information he was offered on Hillary Clinton was part of a Russian government effort</a> to influence the 2016 US election.</p><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">The meeting in June of last year between the President&rsquo;s eldest son and a Russian lawyer occurred at the behest of a Moscow-based singer with family ties to Trump&rsquo;s businesses, according to a participant in the talks.</p><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">Trump Jr has denied anything came of the meeting although his <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2017/07/09/us/donald-trump-jrs-two-different-explanations-for-russian-meeting.html?smid=tw-nytimes&amp;smtyp=cur" target="_blank">story appeared to change a number of times</a> over the weekend.</p><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">But whilst the allegations are potentially juicy, the most interesting aspect is the &ldquo;participant&rdquo; who provided the details in an email.</p><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">Meet Rob Goldstone.</p><br />
<div class="embed-asset embed" data-type="embed-asset" data-provider="Embed" data-title=""><br />
<div class="embed-code"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10154750396497795&set=a.10150279146282795.341803.727067794&type=3&theater" data-iframely-url="//dk79lclgtez2i.cloudfront.net/3rg4Ruk"></a><script async src="//dk79lclgtez2i.cloudfront.net/embed.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></div><br />
     <br />
<h4 class="ap-story-p">1) The Basics</h4><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">Goldstone is a music publicist at <a href="https://www.oui2.com/" target="_blank">Oui 2 Entertainment</a>&nbsp;and set up the meeting on behalf of his client, Emin Agalarov.</p><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">He&rsquo;s British, from Manchester originally but lives in New York.</p><br />
<h4 class="ap-story-p">2) What Else Do We Know About Him?</h4><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">Thankfully, Goldstone appears to be an avid user of social media, from which we can glean a remarkable insight into his life.</p><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">First up, the meeting in question almost certainly did happen because he checked into Trump Tower on the day.</p><br />
<div class="embed-asset embed" data-type="embed-asset" data-provider="Embed" data-title=""><br />
<div class="embed-code"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" align="center"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">You have to love that Rob Goldstone wrote an email saying the Russian gov wants to help beat Hillary and then checked in for the meeting <a href="https://t.co/Ajg1NWHciA">pic.twitter.com/Ajg1NWHciA</a></p>&mdash; Josh Schwerin (@JoshSchwerin) <a href="https://twitter.com/JoshSchwerin/status/884595150810484741">July 11, 2017</a></blockquote><br />
<script async src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></div><br />
     <br />
<h4 class="ap-story-p">3) Has He Met Trump?</h4><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">Yup.&nbsp;</p><br />
<div class="embed-asset embed" data-type="embed-asset" data-provider="Embed" data-title=""><br />
<div class="embed-code"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10154344796652795&set=pb.727067794.-2207520000.1499771875.&type=3&theater" data-iframely-url="//dk79lclgtez2i.cloudfront.net/GUNRjGS"></a><script async src="//dk79lclgtez2i.cloudfront.net/embed.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></div><br />
     <br />
<h4 class="ap-story-p">4) Is There Any Other Evidence Linking Trump And Russia?</h4><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">Well, nothing concrete but just hours after Trump&rsquo;s election victory he posted this since-deleted picture of himself on Instagram with the caption: &ldquo;Hedging bets.&rdquo;</p><br />
<br />
<p class="ap-story-p">And he&rsquo;s a regular visitor to Russia.</p><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">&nbsp;</p><br />
