     <br />
<h4 class="ap-story-p">5) Does He Own An Obscene Hat?</h4><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">Funny you should ask - yes, it appears that he does.</p><br />
<div class="embed-asset embed" data-type="embed-asset" data-provider="Embed" data-title=""><br />
