     <br />
<h4 class="ap-story-p">6) Who Does He Represent?</h4><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">Emin Agalarov, an Azerbaijani crooner who has enjoyed moderate success in Russia and Europe.</p><br />
<div class="embed-asset embed" data-type="embed-asset" data-provider="Embed" data-title=""><br />
<div class="embed-code"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/emin/photos/a.117652234963252.15899.117651834963292/1184300621631736/?type=3&theater" data-iframely-url="//dk79lclgtez2i.cloudfront.net/52mZ8CX"></a><script async src="//dk79lclgtez2i.cloudfront.net/embed.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></div><br />
     <br />
<p class="ap-story-p">His father,&nbsp;Aras, hosted the Miss Universe contest in 2013 whilst Donald Trump was owner of the enterprise.</p><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">Goldstone is also involved in the contests.</p><br />
<div class="embed-asset embed" data-type="embed-asset" data-provider="Embed" data-title=""><br />
<div class="embed-code"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10154607300442795&set=t.727067794&type=3&theater" data-iframely-url="//dk79lclgtez2i.cloudfront.net/r0HktFn"></a><script async src="//dk79lclgtez2i.cloudfront.net/embed.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></div><br />
     <br />
<h4 class="ap-story-p">7) Any Other Links To The Trumps?</h4><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">He&rsquo;s Facebook friends with Lara, wife of Eric Trump.</p><br />
<br />
<h4 class="ap-story-p">8) Has He Ever Made A Phone Call From A Giant Seagull?</h4><br />
<p class="ap-story-p">Why yes, yes he has.</p><br />
