     <br />
<h4>9) Does He Have A Sense Of Humour?</h4><br />
<p>Honestly, his Facebook page is a self-deprecating riot.</p><br />
<div class="embed-asset embed" data-type="embed-asset" data-provider="Embed" data-title=""><br />
